          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1624355494624-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>chestnut mushrooms </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1624355646774-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1624355646774-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1624355646774-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1624355646774-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1624355646774-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>,<strong> pepper </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add 5 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[7 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[10 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>pizza sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1624355501851-x200.jpg",
