      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>,<strong> </strong>then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper<strong> </strong>(squeeze as much liquid out as you can!)</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella </strong>into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Drain your <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1624355506868-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
